data.eml:eml: A new species of Stenopsyche, with descriptions of larvae and females of some species associated by gene sequences (Insecta: Trichoptera)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ji-Hua, Xu, Chang-Hai, Sun, Bei-Xin, Wang (2015): A new species of Stenopsyche, with descriptions of larvae and females of some species associated by gene sequences (Insecta: Trichoptera). Zootaxa 4057 (1): 63-78, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4057.1.3
